Title: Rent
Writer: Diana Gabaldon (based on the series of books written by), Ronald D. Moore (developed by), Toni Graphia (written for television by)
Actors: Caitriona Balfe, Sam Heughan, Tobias Menzies, Graham McTavish
Plot: Claire goes on the road with Dougal as he collects rents from the tenants. She meets the clans solicitor who is riding with them. She also becomes aware of Dougal's involvement in trying to raise money for the Jacobite rebellion.
